/chatter/feed-elements/feedElementId/capabilities/bookmarks

e.g.
/services/data/v48.0/chatter/feed-elements/0D5B0000010S9cHKAS/capabilities/bookmarks

Body
{
  "isBookmarkedByCurrentUser" : false
}

isBookmarkedByCurrentUser set to true to bookmark, false to unbookmark


